---
source: crates/speedrun/src/help.rs
expression: output
---
                                                            
          ┌──────────── Keybindings ────────────┐           
          │ Playback                            │           
          │   Space         Play / pause        │           
          │   + / =         Speed up            │           
          │   -             Speed down          │           
          │                                     │           
          │ Navigation                          │           
          │   ← →           Seek ±5s            │           
          │   Shift+← →     Seek ±30s           │           
          │   . ,           Step forward / back │           
          │   ] [           Next / prev marker  │           
          │   0-9           Jump to 0%-90%      │           
          │   Home / g      Jump to start       │           
          │   End / G       Jump to end         │           
          │                                     │           
          │ Display                             │           
          │   Tab           Toggle controls     │           
          │   ?             Toggle help         │           
          │                                     │           
          │ Application                         │           
          │   q / Esc       Quit                │           
          └─────────────────────────────────────┘
